{"article_id":"1nhaO97yD96qpmvt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Mitt Romney , the former governor of Massachusetts , is now a Senate candidate in Utah -","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"and the announcement of his candidacy shows","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"he ' s sensitive about being labeled a carpetbagger .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"\" Utah , \"","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"the Republican says at the beginning of a video","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"he shared Friday morning on social media ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"\" is admired not only for its beauty , but also for the character of its people .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Utahns are known for hard work , innovation , and our can-do pioneering spirit .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"But more than these , we ' re known as a people","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who serve ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"who care ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and who rise to any occasion . \"","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"It goes on like this for more than two minutes .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"One reporter joked on Twitter","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"that he lost count","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"of how many times Romney said","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"\" Utah. \"","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"The strategy","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"telegraphed in recent days","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"is clear and multipronged :","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Romney ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"who fell short in two previous White House bids","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and emerged as one of Donald Trump ' s fiercest critics ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"is trying to persuade voters","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"that he is laser-focused on his adopted state and not on the president or the job","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"he ' s pined for in the past .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Though on paper this should be a cakewalk","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"- Romney is hardly a stranger in Utah ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"and Democrats have little chance","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"of picking up the seat -","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"two prominent Republicans have made an issue of Romney ' s Trump-bashing and his relocation to the West .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"One of them , State Auditor John Dougall , told","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that GOP activists in and outside Utah have been encouraging him","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"after he said this week","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that he was seriously considering challenging Romney .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"\" Some of the key things in Utah are that we want to make sure","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"we have a senator","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"who understands Utah issues ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and those are clearly different than Massachusetts issues , for instance , \"","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Dougall said Friday morning in a brief telephone interview .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Dougall added","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that Romney had called him Thursday evening","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"to inform him of his imminent announcement ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"which has been anticipated","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"since Sen. Orrin Hatch made his retirement plans known last month .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"\" I wished him all the best , \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Dougall said of Romney .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"A Romney spokesperson did not immediately respond to a request for comment .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"Dougall declined to say","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"who is encouraging him to run .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"But he suggested","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"support would come from those concerned about electing someone","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"who would not be aligned with Trump .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"For weeks on his Facebook page , Dougall has been arguing against a \" coronation \" of Romney .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"\" What we need is not somebody","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"who doesn ' t like the president , \"","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Dougall told .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"the key thing right now is folks need to know","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"what he stands for . \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"After the phone interview , Dougall added via email :","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"\" I should have also mentioned","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"that ' It 's clear that Utahns have a very favorable view of Mr. Romney .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The odds are strongly in his favor . ' \"","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Earlier this week , Utah Republican Party Chair Rob Anderson noted Romney ' s criticism of Trump","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"and spoke dismissively of his Utah credentials in an interview with the Salt Lake Tribune :","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"\" I think","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"he ' s keeping out candidates","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"would be a better fit for Utah","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"because ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"let ' s face it ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Mitt Romney doesn ' t live here ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"his kids weren ' t born here ,","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"he doesn ' t shop here . \"","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"\" I ' ve no doubt","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"that Mitt Romney satisfies all qualifications","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"to run for Senate , \"","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"said Anderson in a Wednesday statement","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"posted on Twitter ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"\" and as chairman of the Utah Republican Party , I will treat all candidates equally","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"to ensure","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"their path to the party nomination is honest and fair . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":167,"left":147,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":100,"right":146,